Motion to enlarge record denied.

The People of the State of New York, Respondent, v Jeffrey Garcia, Appellant. [964 NYS2d 55]

—An appeal having been taken to this Court by the above-named appellant from a judgment of the Supreme Court, New York County (Ronald A. Zweibel, J), rendered on or about June 17, 2011, said appeal having been argued by counsel for the respective parties, due deliberation having been had thereon, and finding the sentence not excessive, it is unanimously ordered that the judgment so appealed from be and the same is hereby affirmed.

Concur— Gonzalez, PJ., Mazzarelli, Moskowitz, Renwick and ManzanetDaniels, JJ.
